Opinion
Per Curiam,
Judgment affirmed. See, Commonwealth v. Wrona, 442 Pa. 201, 275 A. 2d 78 (1971); Commonwealth v. Howard, 426 Pa. 305 (1967); Commonwealth v. Davis, 203 Pa. Superior Ct. 79 (1964) ; Commonwealth v. Zelnick, 202 Pa. Superior Ct. 129 (1963).
Mr. Justice Cohen took no part in the decision of this case.
